<title>JAPAN: Dowa Mining to issue 50 mln Sfr warrant.</title>
<headline>Dowa Mining to issue 50 mln Sfr warrant.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>BORROWER - Dowa Mining Co Ltd</p>
<p>LEAD MGR - Credit Suisse First Boston</p>
<p>GUARANTOR - Industrial Bank of Japan</p>
<p> TYPE   Sfr warrant     ISSUE NO		AMT   50 million Sfr</p>
<p> COUPON		     ISS PRICE	     MATURITY 24.Apr.01</p>
<p> EXERCISE FRM 8.May.97  EXERCISE TO 17.Apr.01</p>
<p> LAST MOODY'S	     PAY DATE 24.Apr.97  INT PAY 24.Apr</p>
<p> LAST S&amp;P		   SIGN DATE 8.Apr.97  SUB DATE</p>
<p> LAST JCR		   LAST JBRI	     LAST NIS</p>
<p>NOTE: The coupon and exercise price will be decided on April 8.</p>
